# CineTracker — project overview

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | SvelteKit 2 + Svelte 5 (runes) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict) |
| CSS | Tailwind CSS v4 |
| UI components | shadcn-svelte (bits-ui) |
| ORM | Prisma v7 + `@prisma/adapter-pg` |
| Database | PostgreSQL (Vercel Postgres / Neon) |
| Auth | Auth.js v1 + `@auth/prisma-adapter` + Google OAuth |
| i18n | Paraglide.js (inlang) |
| Data fetching | `@tanstack/svelte-query` (client-side) |
| Themes | `mode-watcher` |
| Deployment | Vercel adapter |

## External media providers

`ANILIST`, `JIKAN`, `KITSU` — free, no API key required.
`TMDB`, `OMDB`, `TVDB`, `TRAKT` — require a user-supplied API key (stored encrypted in `user_api_keys`).

## Architecture: Feature-Sliced Design

```
src/
  pages/          # pages (home, lists, list-details, media-details, profile, layout, signin)
  features/       # isolated features (theme-toggler, locale-selector)
  widgets/        # composite blocks (app-sidebar)
  shared/
    config/       # domain.ts — WATCH_STATUSES, MEDIA_TYPES, MEDIA_TYPE_META, WATCH_STATUS_META, PROVIDER_META
    lib/          # labels.ts, html.ts — utilities
  lib/
    server/       # server-side logic (providers/, repositories/, external.ts, crypto.ts)
    components/ui/ # shadcn components (button, input, select, sidebar, sheet…)
    paraglide/    # generated runtime
  routes/         # SvelteKit routes (+page.svelte, +page.server.ts, api/**)
```

## Environment variables

```
DATABASE_URL            # PostgreSQL connection string
AUTH_GOOGLE_ID          # Google OAuth client ID
AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET      # Google OAuth client secret
API_KEYS_ENCRYPTION_KEY # 32-byte hex key for AES-256-GCM encryption of provider keys
```
